Game : UEFA Striker 
Date : 2004/10/20 
Video: PAL
Ripped by: DCP
Rip notes: All Languages Except English Ripped

Choose from over 100 teams and 9 different game modes in an effort to win the European & World Cups.
 
All the teams and players can be customised and the commentary, provided by Jonathon Pearce, Ron Atkinson & Ruud Gullit, helps move the action along. 
 
Variable weather conditions, custom formations and tactics are also included as well as the multi-player and training modes. Get out there and bring home the cup.